➜宽哥：《一斛珠.中秋》
http://www.sohu.com/a/422302921_100115135	31397
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201002/59067e491520476284999d6ebc19fd5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>《一斛珠.中秋》词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 原文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中秋佳节，依偎父母同圆月。水调高吟兴难竭。玉饼琼浆，华室温馥郁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘游子思乡烈，琐事总把归期截。今夜惬意双亲说，早夕相牵，嬉戏花间蝶。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201002/ccba4685b869450b959d281492d9914a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201002/24fee04440cf43b1842cee23aec73538.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
