<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>西江月．中秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时令几声一岁，九州万户千盅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中秋国庆共华容，期待丰年欢梦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圆月轻笼清夜，酒香飘入寒宫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问嫦娥玉兔樵农，堪爱人间情重？</p>
