➜广西诗人陈熠明：芳华倚剑梦天娇
http://www.sohu.com/a/422306210_100115135	33026
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201002/89b3462072cf4ee4a883c1b7761ffd01.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>芳华倚剑梦天娇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•天涯倚剑梦江湖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逍遥品醉一征途，水月龙门望古都。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瀚海风云说往事，天涯倚剑梦江湖。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•玉影江边水月娇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流云爱恨泪心潮，玉影江边水月娇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世事遥遥飞影幻，风流剑上问逍遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（三）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•爱恨纷纷世上潮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡远流风顺水飘，鸿途坎坷任逍摇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯漫漫江湖梦，爱恨纷纷世上潮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201002/1862669a0d6c4793bbdc9794b6230ecb.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
